# _bayard тАФ zsh completion for **bayard** тАФ mosuka/bayard, the
#            **distributed full-text search server** built on the
#            canonical pure-Rust Lucene-equivalent search-engine
#            library **tantivy** тАФ  Bayard layers a Raft-replicated
#            cluster + gRPC + HTTP server + dynamic schema management
#            + Japanese / Korean / Chinese tokenization (via
#            `lindera-tantivy`) on top of tantivy's index primitives,
#            producing what is essentially an Elasticsearch-shaped
#            distributed search engine written entirely in safe Rust
