#            peers via the **foca** SWIM gossip-protocol membership
#            crate (the same gossip-membership protocol used by
#            HashiCorp Consul / Memberlist / Cassandra), then routes
#            index + search requests across nodes via a tonic-based
#            gRPC mesh + a public axum HTTP API.  Rust=181 **OPENS**
#            Axis 126 (pure-Rust full-text search / Lucene-equivalent
#            inverted-index engine / **tantivy** ecosystem тАФ
#            `tantivy` + `tantivy-tokenizer-api` + `tantivy-fst` +
