#                                      `LowerCaser`,
#                                      `Stemmer` (with all
#                                      Snowball languages),
#                                      `AsciiFoldingFilter`,
#                                      `AlphaNumOnlyFilter`,
#                                      `StopWordFilter`,
#                                      `SplitCompoundWords`
#     тАв Typed Snowball stemmers        all Lucene-compatible
#                                      Snowball language stemmers
