#                                      primitives + typed
#                                      `collector::FacetCollector`
#                                      hierarchical-facet
#                                      counting (the
#                                      `/electronics/cameras/dslr`
#                                      drill-down pattern)
#     тАв Typed columnar fast fields     (`tantivy-columnar`) for
